00:54:19,536 --> 00:54:23,536
求めることに夢中で
you're so intent on seeking it out.

488
00:54:23,536 --> 00:54:26,936
運命さえまだ知らない
Still unaware of your own fate,

489
00:54:26,936 --> 00:54:30,436
いたいけな瞳
with those innocent eyes.

490
00:54:31,236 --> 00:54:34,636
だけどいつかは気づくでしょう
But someday, you will surely realize

491
00:54:34,636 --> 00:54:38,036
その背中には
that on your back,

492
00:54:38,036 --> 00:54:41,436
遥か未来 めざすための
to aim for the distant future,

493
00:54:41,436 --> 00:54:44,736
羽根があること
you have wings.

494
00:54:46,236 --> 00:54:50,036
残酷な天使のテーゼ
The thesis of a cruel angel

495
00:54:50,036 --> 00:54:53,736
窓辺からやがて飛び立つ
will soon fly out from the window.

496
00:54:53,736 --> 00:54:57,236
ほとばしる熱いパトスで
With a surging, hot pathos,

497
00:54:57,236 --> 00:55:01,236
思い出を裏切るなら
if you betray your memories...

498
00:55:02,278 --> 00:55:04,678
少年よ 神話になれ
Young boy, become a myth!

499
00:55:53,778 --> 00:55:56,878
ずっと眠ってる
Lying asleep forever...

500
00:55:56,878 --> 00:56:00,778
私の愛のゆりかご
...in the cradle of my love.

501
00:56:01,078 --> 00:56:04,078
あなただけが
You alone...

502
00:56:04,078 --> 00:56:06,478
夢の使者に
...by the messenger of dreams...

503
00:56:06,478 --> 00:56:08,778
呼ばれる朝が来る
...will be summoned as morning comes.

504
00:56:09,378 --> 00:56:12,678
細い首筋を
Upon your slender neck,

505
00:56:12,678 --> 00:56:16,178
月あかりが映してる
the moonlight shines down.

506
00:56:16,178 --> 00:56:19,878
世界中の時を止めて
I want to stop time all over the world

507
00:56:19,878 --> 00:56:23,278
閉じ込めたいけど
and lock you in, but...

508
00:56:23,678 --> 00:56:27,278
もしも二人逢えたことに
If there is a meaning

509
00:56:27,278 --> 00:56:31,278
意味があるなら
to the two of us meeting...

510
00:56:31,578 --> 00:56:34,678
私はそう
...then I am, yes,

511
00:56:34,678 --> 00:56:38,378
自由を知るためのバイブル
your bible for learning what freedom is.

512
00:56:38,778 --> 00:56:42,278
残酷な天使のテーゼ
A cruel angel's thesis,

513
00:56:42,278 --> 00:56:46,178
悲しみがそして始まる
sadness will soon begin.

514
00:56:46,278 --> 00:56:49,978
抱きしめた命の形
The shape of the life I embraced,

515
00:56:49,978 --> 00:56:53,478
その夢に目覚めたとき
when you awaken to that dream...

516
00:56:53,478 --> 00:56:57,078
誰よりも光を放つ
...you will shine brighter than anyone else.

517
00:56:57,078 --> 00:57:00,778
少年よ 神話になれ
Young boy, become a myth!

518
00:57:01,378 --> 00:57:05,078
人は愛をつむぎながら
While weaving love,

519
00:57:05,078 --> 00:57:08,578
歴史をつくる
people create history.

520
00:57:08,578 --> 00:57:11,978
女神なんてなれないまま
Without ever becoming a goddess,

521
00:57:11,978 --> 00:57:16,278
私は生きる
I continue to live.

522
00:57:16,378 --> 00:57:19,678
残酷な天使のテーゼ
A cruel angel's thesis

523
00:57:19,678 --> 00:57:23,478
窓辺からやがて飛び立つ
will eventually flutter out from the window.

524
00:57:23,478 --> 00:57:27,078
ほとばしる熱いパトスで
With a surging, hot pathos,

525
00:57:27,078 --> 00:57:30,778
思い出を裏切るなら
if you betray your memories,

526
00:57:30,778 --> 00:57:34,278
この宇宙を抱いて輝く
embrace this sky and shine!

527
00:57:34,278 --> 00:57:38,278
少年よ 神話になれ
Young boy, become a myth!

